    "The learning rate is first warmed up to the set value, and then linearly decayed to 0.",
    "We use 8 80GB Nvidia A100 GPUs for fine-tuning, typically costing 8 hours for Stage 1 and 30 hours for Stage 2.",
    "Following (Chen et al., 2023), we set the maximum sequence length to 8192.",
    "This is because the prompt used to generate the solution tree will exceed 4,500 characters after adding user instructions and descriptions of Tools and APIs, as described in Appendix C.1.3.",
